title: Man's Best Friend 1993 eng ita
description:
Il migliore amico dell'uomo / Man's best friend (1993)

Actors: Robert Costanzo, John Cassini, Lance Henriksen, Allie Sheedy, William Sanderson
Directors: John J. Lafia
Writers: John J. Lafia
Producers: Robert Kosberg, Daniel Grodnik, Robert Engelman
Release dates: November 19, 1993

A genetically mutated dog is accidentally released from the lab of Dr. Jarret and ends up at the home of news reporter/animal rights advocate Lori Tanner. The dog, Max, endowed with intelligence and other special abilities, is at first lovable, but also proves to be a ferocious, unstoppable killer.

Audio: English - Italian
